thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by Daryl

author: Daryl
title: Daryl
text:
I have ordered several different stamps in various sizes and shapes over the past year and I am extremely satisfied. Every order has been on time and correct. Their website makes it very easy to choose and decide on what you want and need. The prices are very competitive.
I will continue to use Rubber Stamp Champ.
